    "content": "You and Me - Lifehouse\r\n\r\nTabbed By: Drew Fish\r\nE-mail: microfish89@yahoo.com\r\n\r\nTuning: Standard\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 2 (in at 0:59)\r\nG|----------------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------10-12-----|\r\nA|----3---2---5-3---3---2-/-7-5-3---10----------|\r\nE|--3---2---0-----3---2------------8--------8\\--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Chorus\r\nG|------------------------------------|\r\nD|------------------------------------|\r\nA|----0-3--------5----0-3--------5----|\r\nE|--3------0-3-0----3------0-3-0---3--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge\r\nG|---------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|--5-4-0----------------------------2------5/9--10--12--13--15--|\r\nA|--------2----2-3--------5--------2---0--5----------------------|\r\nE|-----------2------0-2-3----0-2-3-------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n(Chorus)-see Note below\r\n\r\n[tab]Outro\r\nG|---------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------|\r\nA|----3---2---5-3------------|\r\nE|--3---2---0------3-(fade)--|[/tab]\r\n\r\nNote: When repeating the Chorus following the Bridge, leave the last note out in the Chorus.\r\n\r\nOrder\r\nVerse 2\r\nChorus\r\nBridge\r\nChorus\r\nOutro\r\n\r\n*Bass comes in at 0:59\r\n\r\nBass does not play from 2:08 to 2:29 (During the first repeat of the Chorus following the Bridge).",
